-- BGR Energy Rated `Buy' in New Coverage at Citigroup as Power Market Grows
-- Shiyin Chen
-- 2010-07-08T01:54:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/bgr-energy-rated-buy-in-new-coverage-at-citigroup-as-power-market-grows.html

          
          
             BGR Energy Systems Ltd. was rated
“buy” in new coverage by Citigroup Inc. analyst Venkatesh
Balasubramaniam, who said India’s power deficits present a
“huge opportunity” as the power generation equipment market is
set to expand.  
 The analyst has a share-price estiamte of 884 rupees.  
